app_description: This is UltraBoard for Business. WhiteBoard BlackBoard ChalkBoard App. A UltraBoard for Business license is required to access this app. Please touch the screen with Apple Pencil stylus pen or your finger. You can change the line color with buttons and the line width with slider. You can save and categorize make folder for each note board.
